  <filename class="directory">/usr/X11R6/man</filename>, etc.). Be sure
  to add these locations to the file <filename>/etc/man_db.conf</filename>, as
  <envar>MANDATORY_MANPATH</envar> <replaceable>&lt;/path&gt;</replaceable>
  lines.</para>
